Interface CodelistMapper

All Known Implementing Classes:
CodelistMapperImpl
public interface CodelistMapper

Codelist gRPC Mapper

MapStruct mapper for codelist-service gRPC communication. Transforms projections to gRPC request messages and response messages to lookup data. Handles codelist key building for batch lookups of localized values. Uses @AfterMapping hooks to dynamically construct codelist keys based on available data.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček
